Things that are done in this project:
-------------------------------------

1. Custom exception class and its exception handler
2. Provide HATEOAS for further actions
3. Location URL for the POST requests
4. Validators like @NotEmpty, @Size(min=2)
5. @JsonProperty("") for showing field names different in response and request than from in object
6. Filtering - static - @JsonIgnore
             - dynamic - @JsonFilter ( used in Employee controller)